{
  "stem": "15028.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Fishov had a son, Moishe Fishov, my age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was already in late July, August or July, in the summer time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] his son got also very weak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was a tall man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was also becoming-- getting there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People were falling every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People were dying in the camp, and at work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He went over to the obersturmfuhrer in the evening somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had a courage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He could have gotten killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he had a discussion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He spoke-- very intelligent man, that Fishov.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He spoke a very perfect German, excellent German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and the man was an old man, the Gestapo, obersturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I can see him today with white hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he told them that you have young people here, like my age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You've got to-- and you're killing their purpose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You're killing them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the Reich is losing out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The German people are losing out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Instead, you should teach them a trade, and put them to work, and make something out of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they'll give you many years to existing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, somehow, it penetrated on Hashem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Somehow, he listened to Hashem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was a religious man, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the next morning, we went on the appellplatz, and not [INAUDIBLE] look at the papers, or the age, or asking.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They just went through us, you know, the Gestapo, and looked at the faces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was one of them picked out to learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And his son, Moishe, was also picked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We went, and they opened up a barrack, a special barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they brought machinery to teach us a trade [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Locksmith.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a lifesaver for a couple of weeks, about six weeks, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
